{"tid":600073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨主席：23條立法若做好諮詢　社會較大機會達共識","createTime":"2018-03-21T04:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T06:28:50.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2149df809c31326d308b89a2c4ff9b85ecaa910b","tid":600073,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:14:16.000Z","msg":"胡志偉今日就23條立法表達立場，稱政府若經充分諮詢有機會達成共識，「如果你能吸納教訓，做好應有的諮詢過程，令整個立法不會令香港市民擔心以言入罪的事情。通過立法過程會做得到的話，我覺得尋找到共識的機會大很多」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指23條立法若寬鬆處理，不致於引起公眾恐慌，「如果能夠找到路徑處理這政治制度的問題，23條立法若用比較寬鬆的處理，不會令市民覺得出現以言入罪，影響言論自由、新聞自由的話，我覺得這問題其實不會令公眾引起恐慌」。"},{"pid":"82b543f683c3dce46d2c4576edd1352937914f45","tid":600073,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af78da0f1b793d301971cb0c865e7da0dac571bb","tid":600073,"uid":59898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"已經演變為主動跪低<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e204926ac4136a032bdae8ceead5e729cfbdce6d","tid":600073,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"五毛狗即刻死入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e6a98c7ee92faa92b78987b0cdc9ed52af3076","tid":600073,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:18:52.000Z","msg":"爭做焦土派 咁既人都有"},{"pid":"238c9b87ddfc3dd74348630a25efe1fa4314626a","tid":600073,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:19:49.000Z","msg":"民主黨：市民喜迎23條立法"},{"pid":"7365a036d48df7f0c91c114974f8b1fe75d2f7e2","tid":600073,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-2